data.description: Within 3 minutes to the public boat ramp. Spacious 2bd-2bth-2gar with large office that has a built-in desk. Huge living area with wbfp and built-in shelves. Separate dining room off of a u-shaped kitchen. All appliances stay including the washer and dryer. Utility room has built in cabinets and pantry. Large bedrooms and a walk-in closet that has a built in safe. This home has an abundance of cabinets offering plenty of storage space. Open pasture behind the home offers a nice view and privacy to enjoy the huge, enclosed patio. Plenty of parking available for boat or RV. Located near lake and community campground with park. Propane tank is owned and used for the central heat only. Nice size lot with mature trees on a cul-de-sac. Storage shed and fenced in garden in the back yard. This is a must see to appreciate. TV mounts stay. Motivated seller. Please bring your offers.
